Repeating the same study a lot of times

. . . For-loop .

mean.samples <- double()
for (it in 1:1e4){
  mean.samples[it] <- mean(sample(pop, size=10))
}
hist(mean.samples, breaks=50, main="Means of Samples (N=10)")

( mn.mn.samples10 <- mean(mean.samples) )
## [1] 100.0255
( sd.mn.samples10 <- sd(mean.samples) )
## [1] 4.743338
